  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The efficacy of risedronate in prevention of bone loss in patients receiving high dose
      corticosteroid treatment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      We compare the effect of risedronate with placebo in bone mineral density changes in patients
      receiving high dose corticosteroids for their underlying diseases
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
